<HR>I noticed that after the patch, the merchant in The Bauble in Neriak no longers sells jewelry and metal bars.  Instead, he sells a fine selection of gems.<P>On the down side, this means that the only place (so far as I know) to buy metal bars in Neriak is from the ogre in the foreign quarter (Shiney Tings).  This means that the price is increased for Dark Elves.<P>If anyone knows of someone else who sells metal bars in Neriak please post that information.
</FONT>
